Earl Agustin channels pop, cool R&B and bits of tasty soul on this mid-tempo bop. Earl Agustin, through Vicor Music, brings back 70’s styled soul music through this catchy tune about falling in love.
#tibok  #ashbin #earlagustin

Mastered by Leon Zervos

Production House: Viva Recording Studios

Label: Vicor Records
